<li>Thomson-Jones, Katherine, 2014,
 <a href="http://www.oxfordbibliographies.com/view/document/obo-9780195396577/obo-9780195396577-0071.xml" target="other">Philosophy of Film</a>,
 in <em>Oxford Bibliographies Online</em>.</li>

