 <li><a href="http://www.dam.org" target="other">Digital Art Museum</a></li>
 
 <li><a href="http://rhizome.org/artbase/" target="other">Rhizome&rsquo;s Artbase</a>,
 the largest on-line archive of new media art</li>

 <li><a href="http://www.vam.ac.uk/page/d/digital-art-and-design/" target="other">Digital Art &amp; Design &ndash; Victoria and Albert Museum</a>,
 information on the history and practice of computer art and
design.</li>

 <li><a href="http://whitney.org/artport/" target="other">The Whitney Museum&rsquo;s Art Port</a>,
 providing access to the museum&rsquo;s collection of digital art and
an exhibition space for commissioned works of net art.</li>
</ul>
